  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Right now we require a percentage increase on the effective priority fee per gas. This causes undesirable properties because most txs stuck in the pool and eligible for replacement will have an effective priority fee per gas of 0. That means that the price bump will be 0. We should require a bump of both the feeCap and maxPriorityFeePerGas.",
